  "body": " Sierpiński space  The Sierpiński space is the set equipped with the topology . Note that this is not the discrete or concrete topology on . After developing the language of conntinuity, we will discover that for an arbitrary topological space , the continuous functions are in natural bijection with open subsets of .  "
