  "body": " Topologies on a finite set  Determine all topologies on the set . How many are there? Now do the same thing with . (You should draw a picture and it should be large and glorious. How can you organize your picture so that it demonstrates important relations between topologies?)  It is an open problem to determine the number of topologies on a finite set (as a function of cardinality). You can find known data and references on this problem on the OEIS .  "
